'''Nathaniel Christopher Brown''' (born 16 June 2003) is a German professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[left-back]] for {{German football updater|EinFrank}} club [[Eintracht Frankfurt]] and the [[Germany national football team|Germany national team]].

==Club career==
Brown is a youth product of TSV Kümmersbruck and [[SSV Jahn Regensburg|Jahn Regensburg]], before joining [[1. FC Nürnberg|Nürnberg]]'s youth academy in 2016.<ref name="auto">{{Cite web|url=https://www.nordbayern.de/sport/1-fc-nuernberg/heimatbesuch-in-der-oberpfalz-club-talent-brown-will-auf-dem-boden-bleiben-1.13389710|title=Heimatbesuch in der Oberpfalz: Club-Talent Brown will "auf dem Boden bleiben"|website=www.nordbayern.de}}</ref> On 15 June 2022, he signed his first professional contract with Nürnberg.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.fcn.de/news/artikel/nathaniel-brown-unterschreibt-profi-vertrag/|title=Nathaniel Brown unterschreibt Profi-Vertrag|website=fcn.de}}</ref> He began his senior career with [[1. FC Nürnberg II|Nürnberg's reserves]] in 2022 in the [[Regionalliga]]. On 10 March 2023, he debuted with the senior Nürnberg team in a 2–0 [[2. Bundesliga]] win over [[Eintracht Braunschweig]] as a late substitute.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.onetz.de/sport/kuemmersbruck/kuemmersbrucker-brown-erstem-zweitliga-einsatz-beim-1-fc-nuernberg-id4005801.html|title=Kümmersbrucker Brown mit erstem Zweitliga-Einsatz beim 1. FC Nürnberg|website=www.onetz.de}}</ref> On 27 June 2023, he extended professional contract with Nürnberg.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.fraenkischertag.de/ueberregional/bayern/1-fc-nuernberg-verlaengert-mit-talent-brown-art-267730|title=1. FC Nürnberg verlängert mit Talent Brown|date=27 June 2023|website=www.fraenkischertag.de}}</ref>

On 3 January 2024, Brown signed for [[Bundesliga]] club [[Eintracht Frankfurt]] on a five-and-a-half-year deal, returning to Nürnberg on loan for the remainder of the season.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://profis.eintracht.de/news/eintracht-frankfurt-verpflichtet-nathaniel-brown-155864|trans-title=Eintracht Frankfurt signs Nathaniel Brown|title=Eintracht Frankfurt verpflichtet Nathaniel Brown|language=German|website=profis.eintracht.de|date=3 January 2024|accessdate=3 January 2024}}</ref> On 2 November 2024, he scored his first Bundesliga goal in a 7–2 victory over [[VfL Bochum|Bochum]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://profis.eintracht.de/2024-2025/bundesliga/spielplan/eintracht-frankfurt-vfl-bochum-1848/spielbericht/ |title=Schützenfest im Stadtwald |publisher=Eintracht Frankfurt |language=de |date=2 November 2024 }}</ref> He was voted his club's Player of the Season for [[2025–26 Eintracht Frankfurt season|2025–26]], having recorded four goals and four assists in the league, as well as two assists in the [[2025–26 UEFA Champions League|UEFA Champions League]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://en.eintracht.de/news/nathaniel-brown-ist-spieler-der-saison-177832 |title=Nathaniel Brown named Player of the Season |publisher=Eintracht Frankfurt |date=4 June 2026 }}</ref>

==International career==
Brown was born in Germany to an American father and German mother.<ref name="auto"/> He is a youth international for Germany, having played for the [[Germany national under-21 football team|Germany U21]]s.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.express.de/sport/fussball/u21-kader-fc-profi-trifft-auf-zwei-koelner-kollegen-637839|title=U21-Nationalmannschaft: Erster Kader nach EM-Debakel: FC-Profi trifft auf zwei Kölner Kollegen|date=1 September 2023|website=EXPRESS}}</ref> In October 2025, he was named to the German [[Germany national football team|senior squad]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dfb.de/news/ein-neuling-und-fuenf-rueckkehrer-fuer-luxemburg-und-nordirland|title=Ein Neuling und fünf Rückkehrer für Luxemburg und Nordirland|publisher=[[German Football Association]]|language=de|access-date=2 October 2025}}</ref> On 10 October 2025, he made his debut for the senior team after coming on as a substitute in a 4–0 win over [[Luxembourg national football team|Luxembourg]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.transfermarkt.de/nurnberg-erhalt-nachzahlung-nach-browns-dfb-debut-ablose-konnte-weiter-steigen/view/news/461547|title=Nürnberg erhält Nachzahlung nach Browns DFB-Debüt – Ablöse könnte weiter steigen|publisher=transfermarkt.de|language=de|access-date=11 October 2025}}</ref>

In May 2026, Brown was named in the 26-man squad for the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.dfb.de/news/nagelsmann-reveals-26-man-squad-for-the-fifa-world-cup |title=Nagelsmann reveals 26-man squad for the FIFA World Cup |publisher=[[German Football Association]] |date=May 21, 2026 |access-date=May 21, 2026 |url-status=live |archive-date=May 21, 2026 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20260521152650/https://www.dfb.de/news/nagelsmann-reveals-26-man-squad-for-the-fifa-world-cup}}</ref>

